info.description:
### About Anthropic

AI research and products that put safety at the frontier.

### Prerequisites

- Postman Account
    
- Anthropic Account: [https://console.anthropic.com/](https://console.anthropic.com/)
    

### Usage

1. Create a fork
    
2. Update collection variables
    
3. Send requests
    

### Documentation

- API: [https://www.anthropic.com/api](https://www.anthropic.com/api)
    
- Models: [https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/about-claude/models](https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/about-claude/models)

            "text": "This image shows a technical architecture diagram for a Context-Aware Multimodal Reasoning Application. It illustrates the flow and components of a large language model and retrieval-augmented generation system.

The diagram is divided into two main sections:
1. Real-time User Interactions (left side)
2. Batch ETL Processes (right side)

Key components include:
- A Chatbot/Voicebot interface (using Gradio)
- RAG (Retrieval & Generation) Platform using LangChain
- AI Platform with multiple modules:
  - Speech-to-Text (Whisper)
  - Text Embedding
  - Image Embedding (CLIP)
  - Text-and-Image-to-Text
  - Text-to-Speech
  - Text-to-Image (Dall-E)
- Vector Store (MongoDB Atlas)
- Guardrail Platform
- Governance Platform

The diagram shows the data flow with numbered steps (1-9) and lettered processes (A-F), explaining how data moves through the system, from user input to final output, including various transformations and safety checks along the way.

The system appears designed to handle multiple types of input (text, audio, image, video) and can perform various conversions and generations between these modalities while maintaining governance and security controls."
        }
